    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗冲锋的故事背景是地球被变异的昆虫彻底占领，人类处于绝境之中。你是一名孤独的幸存者，需要在文明的废墟中搜寻物资、揭开地球被昆虫占领的秘密，玩家利用各种变异昆虫的特性在绝境中挣扎求生和绝地反击。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界，先活下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感染敌人<br>使用特殊能力寄生变异昆虫甚至操控他们。渗透虫群内部、揭开谜底，找到让变异昆虫自相残杀的办法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/c9beb74c507d683fcb3bffa438ea965d.poster.avif?t=1764851590\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/c9beb74c507d683fcb3bffa438ea965d.webm?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/c9beb74c507d683fcb3bffa438ea965d.mp4?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>接受变异</strong><br>这是一个可怕的变异过程，你的身体将会与昆虫基因融合，并获得更为强大能力——或许你不再是一个真正的人类。人类与异虫已经无法分清。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/c5ac05a8179068f8010f8065ce09163d.poster.avif?t=1764851590\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/c5ac05a8179068f8010f8065ce09163d.webm?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/c5ac05a8179068f8010f8065ce09163d.mp4?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>操控天气作为武器</strong> <br>利用强大的 HAARP 系统操控天气。释放雷暴、暴雪和电磁脉冲来消灭变异昆虫，掌握战争走向，逆转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/b8da32626404b65ab7ba783db40db2f9.poster.avif?t=1764851590\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/b8da32626404b65ab7ba783db40db2f9.webm?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/b8da32626404b65ab7ba783db40db2f9.mp4?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>揭开外星阴谋</strong><br>传言都是真的：HAARP 正在运作，黑暗秩序真的存在。 你需要解开一个又一个的阴谋与背叛，彻底解开这个埋藏真相的世界，这个秘密甚至能决定地球的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索绝望的废墟，对抗无尽的虫群，收集资源、进化、变异，在人性与兽性无法分清的世界中，冲出自己的道路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/4a20dc167a08c6413fdeb9d8fee02454.poster.avif?t=1764851590\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/4a20dc167a08c6413fdeb9d8fee02454.webm?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/4a20dc167a08c6413fdeb9d8fee02454.mp4?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诡异而沉浸的场景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭在这个被外星生物摧毁的地球，探索因气候实验而变得寒冷可怕的废弃都市，找到那个秘密的军事地堡，以及被变异虫群占领的废墟，和异虫的地下巢穴。每个异虫群落都各不相同，你需要不停的探索和找到拯救地球的办法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/3fd963c13de73ac0bf1bf713123983de.poster.avif?t=1764851590\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/3fd963c13de73ac0bf1bf713123983de.webm?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1363400/extras/3fd963c13de73ac0bf1bf713123983de.mp4?t=1764851590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br> <br>游戏特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术第三人称生存射击</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要选择不同的暗黑分支剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的寄生机制操控敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于 HAARP 的动态天气系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >异虫变异系统与升级系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡制科幻、恐怖的沉寂式场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个外星阴谋与昆虫末日暗黑世界</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>你能以人类的方式活下去，还是彻底成为异虫的一部分。</strong></p>",
